---
title: Plan Mode
type: app
version: 1
created: 2026-02-27
status: active
---

::filter-bar[target="#task-board"]
- Status (select: All | To Do | In Progress | Done)
- Priority (select: All | Low | Medium | High)
::

::board[source="/api/tasks/board"]
columns: To Do | In Progress | Done
card-template: {= title =} @{= assignee =}
::

::action[method=post target="/api/tasks" label="Add Task"]
- Name (text) *
- Priority (select: Low | Medium | High)
- Type (select: Feature | Bug | Chore)
::

::search[source="/api/research/search" placeholder="Search articles..."]
::

::dashboard[source="/api/grow/metrics" refresh=60]
::

::feed[source="/api/chat/messages" stream]
::
